com.vmware.vapi.std.introspection

Interface ProviderSyncProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProviderTypes, Service

    public interface ProviderSyncProvider
extends Service, ProviderTypes
    The ProviderSyncProvider service provides operations to retrieve information about a vAPI Provider. A provider is a container that exposes one or more vAPI services.
